CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 21, 1970, pg. 14 reads: "On Target - Chris Eleam, one of the key performers on the high flying Fifth Avenue High School basketball team, drives the baseline for a two pointer in Fifth's easy victory against Allderdice last week. Rated as one of the top high school quintets in state, Fifth is currently unbeaten in City League play...Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Basketball game between Allderdice High School, and Fifth Avenue High School, including #11 Chris Eleam shooting ball, in gymnasium
